subj.title: [This article](http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/9906064) was referenced by ["Top Cited Articles during 2009 in hep-th"](http://www.slac.stanford.edu/spires/topcites/2009/eprints/to_hep-th_annual.shtml) on Monday, March  8 2010.
[This article](http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/9906064) was referenced by ["Extra Dimensions"](http://backreaction.blogspot.com/2006/07/extra-dimensions.html) on Wednesday, July 12 2006.

[This article](http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/9906064) was referenced by ["symmetry breaking » Blog Archive » 2009 TopCites: 50 most-cited articles in high-energy physics"](http://www.symmetrymagazine.org/breaking/2010/03/08/2009-topcites-50-most-cited-articles-in-high-energy-physics/) on Monday, March  8 2010.

[This article](http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/9906064) was referenced by ["Top Cited Articles of All Time (2009 edition) in hep-th"](http://www.slac.stanford.edu/spires/topcites/2009/eprints/to_hep-th_alltime.shtml) on Monday, March  8 2010.

[This article](http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/9906064) was referenced by ["symmetry breaking » Blog Archive » Top-cited high-energy physics articles during 2008"](http://www.symmetrymagazine.org/breaking/2009/01/14/top-cited-high-energy-physics-articles-during-2008/) on Thursday, January  1 2009.

[This article](http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/9906064) was referenced by ["Why three dimensions of space just aren't enough"](http://preposterousuniverse.blogspot.com/2004_12_01_preposterousuniverse_archive.html#110201245713210741) on Friday, March 17 2006.

[This article](http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/9906064) was referenced by ["arxiv Find:  Cycling in the Throat"](http://cosmicvariance.com/2007/02/03/arxiv-find-cycling-in-the-throat/) on Sunday, February  4 2007.

[This article](http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/9906064) was referenced by ["Searching for Things Not Named “Higgs” Part I: Micro Black Holes"](http://www.quantumdiaries.org/2012/03/15/not-higgs/) on Monday, March 19 2012.
